&lt;NEW&gt;

&quot;BAH!&quot; SCOURGE said as he watched STRAIGHT SHOT undergo her
transformation and become something else. &quot;This is foolishness.&quot; There
was no fear that could be seen on SCOURGE but there did seem to be a
growing sense of annoyance and impatience on his part. He was mumbling
something about him being a warrior and not a slaggin spy.

&quot;Come on!&quot; he said obviously talking to his sweeps and perhaps
WASPINATOR as he turned away from NIGHTSHIFT and the newly changed
Maximal, he was still carrying the strange alien device that DARK
RODIMUS had dropped. &quot;Maybe this can help us find out where he went.&quot;
There was a chuckle, &quot;*IF* he made it.&quot;

They began to fly into the air, one sweep following SCOURGE and the
other two going off in a different direction - the same direction that
CYCLONUS and RODIMUS had taken.

Around them the other Predacons were pulling out as well, heading off
into the distance. WASPINATOR just sighed and followed as well.

